map._queryString:
{[date]
   res: select last Date, Lat: first(Lat), Long:first(Long), sum(Confirmed), sum(Deaths), sum(Recovered), sum(ConfirmedDelta), Opacity: 0.75, Ratio: ratios[sum(Confirmed); 100] +6  by Country_Region from CovidOpenData where Date = date;
  
   select Country_Region, Date, Lat, Long, Confirmed, Deaths, Recovered,ConfirmedDelta, Ratio, Active: ((Confirmed - Deaths) - Recovered),
      RecoveredRate: (Recovered * 100)  div Confirmed,
      DeathsRate: (Deaths * 100) div Confirmed,
      ActiveRate: (((Confirmed - Deaths) - Recovered )* 100) div Confirmed
      from res where Lat <> 0
 }
